high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the window, and then turn right towards the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Slice the front lettuce in half.
Turn around and head towards the cabinet to the right of the oven.
Open the cabinet and place the knife in it.
Turn around and head towards the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the lettuce.
Turn right, walk towards the door, and then turn left to open the fridge.
Place the lettuce to the left of the pan in the fridge, close the fridge for the lettuce to cool down, and then pick the lettuce out of the fridge.
Turn left towards the sink and then turn right towards the toaster on the counter.
Place the lettuce to the right of the knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled slice of lettuce to the right of the knife.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk over to the kitchen counter where the dishwasher is.
Pick up the metal butter knife off of the counter.
Use the metal butter knife to slice up the closest head of lettuce.
Turn right and take a step, then turn right again to face the kitchen counter.
Open the lower right cabinet door and place the metal butter knife inside.
Turn around and walk back over to the sliced head of lettuce.
Pick up a piece of sliced lettuce.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then stop once at the fridge and turn left.

Open the fridge door and place the piece of sliced lettuce on the second rack from the bottom, and close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge door, remove the piece of sliced lettuce, and close the door.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the toaster on the kitchen counter.
Place the chilled piece of sliced lettuce onto the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled piece of sliced lettuce on the counter in front of the toaster.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the end of the counter and turn right.
Pick the knife on the counter up.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Turn around to the bottom cabinet just to the right of the cook stove.
Put the knife on the bottom shelf of the cupboard.
Shut the cabinet door and turn back to the lettuce.
Pick up a slice of lettuce off of the counter.
Turn to the right and walk down to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the lettuce on the middle rack and close the door, wait a little bit and then open the door again and take the lettuce back out.
Turn to the left and walk to the cabinet on the left that is on the left side of the cook stove.
Put the lettuce on the cabinet just to the right of the knife and spatula .
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of lettuce on the counter beside the cook stove.
